two chicken ramen

324
00:20:31.231 --> 00:20:32.232
so that's what you're getting.

325
00:20:32.232 --> 00:20:33.775
Uh-uh. Nah. fool. Nah. man.

326
00:20:33.775 --> 00:20:35.360
