hots. man. Give me those hots.

327
00:20:36.152 --> 00:20:39.114
BOSCO: <i>Lunch? Probably
a cream bologna sandwich</i>

328
00:20:39.114 --> 00:20:41.991
<i>and an apple that's been
kicked around for extra flavor.</i>

329
00:20:41.991 --> 00:20:44.452
