417
00:27:02.372 --> 00:27:05.250
Entering your cell. 759.

418
00:27:05.250 --> 00:27:07.085
Sit.

419
00:27:10.088 --> 00:27:12.424
BOSCO: <i>Even with my
special treatment.</i>

420
00:27:12.424 --> 00:27:14.134
