<i>You're in a box. bro.</i>

468
00:30:14.731 --> 00:30:16.649
BOSCO:
<i>He's right.</i>

469
00:30:16.649 --> 00:30:18.443
<i>I need a direct line.</i>

470
00:30:20.820 --> 00:30:23.031
♪ ♪

471
00:30:25.742 --> 00:30:30.372
<i>Truth is.
it's hard to get shit in here.</i>

472
00:30:30.372 --> 00:30:31.998
<i>But desperation finds a way.</i>

473
00:30:31.998 --> 00:30:34.542
