on the outside.</i>

475
00:30:36.169 --> 00:30:37.962
<i>and credit with The Bull
is twice that.</i>

476
00:30:38.880 --> 00:30:40.590
<i>But if you want something
that you can't buy</i>

477
00:30:40.590 --> 00:30:43.968
<i>from the prison pimps--
drugs. weapons. info--</i>

478
00:30:43.968 --> 00:30:46.846
<i>shit. tools like the ones
I need.</i>

479
00:30:46.846 --> 00:30:48.556
<i>you gotta go fishing...</i>

480
00:30:50.558 --> 00:30:52.769
<i>and...</i>

481
00:30:52.769 --> 00:30:55.397
<i>make it yourself.</i>

482
00:30:58.566 --> 00:31:02.696
<i>Every item I get. my bill
goes up with The Bull. so...</i>

483
00:31:02.696 --> 00:31:05.281
<i>gotta make it worth it.</i>

484
00:31:05.281 --> 00:31:07.117
<i>I always was good at puzzles.</i>

485
00:31:07.117 --> 00:31:08.410
(keypad beeping)

486
00:31:09.911 --> 00:31:11.246
(buzzer sounds)

487
00:31:14.833 --> 00:31:16.835
(keys jingling)

488
00:31:16.835 --> 00:31:18.628
(line ringing)

489
00:31:18.628 --> 00:31:21.214
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>You have a collect call.</i>

490
00:31:24.050 --> 00:31:26.386
(keypad beeping)

491
00:31:27.679 --> 00:31:29.556
(line ringing)

492
00:31:30.515 --> 00:31:33.435
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>You have a collect call from...</i>

493
00:31:44.612 --> 00:31:46.740
